data.description: Check out this stunning waterfront paradise nestled along the serene St. Lucie River! This remarkable property boasts a generous .47-acre river front deep water lot, offering tranquility and quick access to the open water with no fixed bridges. Sitting across from a private preserve, Its stunning features and meticulous details presents an extraordinary opportunity for the discerning buyer or Investor (NO HOA) seeking the ultimate Florida lifestyle. Enjoy the convenience of navigating the St. Lucie River with ease from your very own extended canopy-covered boat dock and lift, rated up to 180mph. Step inside and be greeted by updated flooring and fresh paint that exude coastal elegance.This home's sleek metal roof, Impact windows offer security, paver walkway leads past the screened in pool to your boat dock. Extended driveway and large garage are great for all your water toys. Don't miss the chance to own this exceptional waterfront retreat!
